    {
      "id": "601685",
      "is_folded": false,
      "answerer": {
        "username": "Nowornever",
        "uid": "103578"
      },
      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t訴求一起步就太”政治化”會嚇退很多人<br/>\n雖然生活著就有政治<br/>\n但很多人此刻出來真的只是蹩太久了<br/>\n先用民生口號凝聚力量<br/>\n當政府維穩手段越漸激烈<br/>\n人們才會真正覺醒問題都在黨<br/>\n到那時候才喊反共口號才會一呼百應\t\t</div>",
      "date": "2022-11-27",
      "agree_count": 16,
      "discussion_count": 0,
      "discussions": []
    },
    {
      "id": "601677",
      "is_folded": false,
      "answerer": {
        "username": "efswefewfwg",
        "uid": "90065"
      },
      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t反共其实是可以的，但是得大规模，要规模大到共产党没办法扑灭的地步，<br/>\n要有肉身和中共抗争到死的决心，而这往往得要有成建制的军队才行\t\t</div>",
      "date": "2022-11-27",
      "agree_count": 6,
      "discussion_count": 0,
      "discussions": []
    },
    {
      "id": "601675",
      "is_folded": false,
      "answerer": {
        "username": "血染长安街",
        "uid": "13998"
      },
      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t首先我问一句，为什么不能反对中国政府？游行的人不都希望政府能撤销错误政策并付出代价吗？\t\t</div>",
      "date": "2022-11-27",
      "agree_count": 8,
      "discussion_count": 0,
      "discussions": []
    },
    {
      "id": "601709",
      "is_folded": false,
      "answerer": {
        "username": "齊心大筆人人插",
        "uid": "98803"
      },
      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t别躲在键盘后面微操上街的人，这不是你的革命游戏，要想做领袖就身先士卒走在前面，不要一天一个的帮别人发明口号发明纲领，这么想做圣雄你上啊\t\t</div>",
      "date": "2022-11-28",
      "agree_count": 5,
      "discussion_count": 0,
      "discussions": []
    },
    {
      "id": "601697",
      "is_folded": false,
      "answerer": {
        "username": "爱娴",
        "uid": "96773"
      },
      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t建议不要一开始就喊共产党下台、习近平下台之类的口号，应该学会就事论事。这类口号只能吓跑很多中国人而且给中共留下镇压的口实。而且中国内陆一些地方的方言根基很大，特别是川渝地区（这也是阿姨提倡发明大蜀民族的原因之一），在当地举行的群众游行活动的时候应该找当地人组织和参加，而且呼口号应该用当地方言而非普通话，用普通话喊口号只能引发当地人的不信任。\t\t</div>",
      "date": "2022-11-27",
      "agree_count": 5,
      "discussion_count": 0,
      "discussions": []
    },
    {
      "id": "601753",
      "is_folded": false,
      "answerer": {
        "username": "雙加不好的鴨語者",
        "uid": "22079"
      },
      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t放心吧！我們要相信政府！<br/>\n<a href=\"url/link/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuY3VwLmNvbS5oay8yMDIwLzAyLzE3L3d1dGphbmt5dW4tZXAxMi8\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://www.cup.com.hk/2020/02/17/wutjankyun-ep12/\">https://www.cup.com.hk/2020/02/17/wutjankyun-ep12/</a><br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9PVnl4NnpILmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/OVyx6zH.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/OVyx6zH.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/OVyx6zH.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9aM3J0Q0N5LmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/Z3rtCCy.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/Z3rtCCy.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Z3rtCCy.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9OaHlKNTVVLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/NhyJ55U.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/NhyJ55U.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/NhyJ55U.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9tM2ZlSG1qLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/m3feHmj.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/m3feHmj.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/m3feHmj.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9jZ1lJMVZNLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/cgYI1VM.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/cgYI1VM.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/cgYI1VM.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS94YkgyalUwLmpwZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/xbH2jU0.jpg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/xbH2jU0.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/xbH2jU0.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a> </div>",
      "date": "2022-11-28",
      "agree_count": 2,
      "discussion_count": 0,
      "discussions": []
    },
    {
      "id": "601693",
      "is_folded": false,
      "answerer": {
        "username": "tuyouyou",
        "uid": "101697"
      },
      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t策略的重点不应是口号精不精致，再精巧也是秀才遇到兵，而是如何迅速的壮大自己，巨硕到让对方无法撼动。\t\t</div>",
      "date": "2022-11-27",
      "agree_count": 4,
      "discussion_count": 0,
      "discussions": []
    },
    {
      "id": "601711",
      "is_folded": false,
      "answerer": {
        "username": "含住棒棒糖",
        "uid": "100597"
      },
      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t很正常，这场抗议本来就没有什么明确的诉求，就是被封了好几年了借火灾事件出来发泄一下。而且上海还有共产党内鬼再带节奏喊习近平下台，这下你看普通人哪里还敢参加你们的抗议？今天星期一大家都要上班上学了，抗议自然就熄火了\t\t</div>",
      "date": "2022-11-28",
      "agree_count": 2,
      "discussion_count": 0,
      "discussions": []
    },
    {
      "id": "601716",
      "is_folded": false,
      "answerer": {
        "username": "s65883",
        "uid": "103530"
      },
      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t建议先拿下各个地区的卫视和电台，把游行的目的和意义广告告知。号召义士在同一时间拉响防空警报。\t\t</div>",
      "date": "2022-11-28",
      "agree_count": 1,
      "discussion_count": 0,
      "discussions": []
    },
    {
      "id": "601683",
      "is_folded": false,
      "answerer": {
        "username": "总钻风",
        "uid": "103468"
      },
      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t1.有明确且切合实际的诉求：<br/>\n<br/>\n结束封控 罢免习近平<br/>\n<br/>\n2.有时间预期去实现目标以定人心：<br/>\n<br/>\n在明年两会和二十届二中三中全会上，习近平辞任一切党内职务，明年两会不连任国家主席。<br/>\n<br/>\n在这四个月内，大家和平抗议，寻求最大公约数，吸引更多人加入，实现这两个诉求。\t\t</div>",
      "date": "2022-11-27",
      "agree_count": 2,
      "discussion_count": 1,
      "discussions": [
        {
          "id": "1129077",
          "replier": {
            "username": "liliwanglili",
            "uid": "16892"
          },
          "date": "2022-11-27",
          "content": "提一个不切实际的大目标无助于实现解封这一最迫切的需要。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "601682",
      "is_folded": false,
      "answerer": {
        "username": "fkccp7410",
        "uid": "103330"
      },
      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t抗议的燃料是清零造成的经济崩溃及各种次生灾难，什么时候清零政策彻底终结了什么时候抗议才可能终止。当然社会问题没解决下一次抗议也就不远了。\t\t</div>",
      "date": "2022-11-27",
      "agree_count": 1,
      "discussion_count": 0,
      "discussions": []
    },
    {
      "id": "601761",
      "is_folded": false,
      "answerer": {
        "username": "arsingsoa",
        "uid": "101392"
      },
      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t这周上海降温下暴雨 老天爷都看不下 变天了 已经熄火 了\t\t</div>",
      "date": "2022-11-28",
      "agree_count": 1,
      "discussion_count": 0,
      "discussions": []
    },
    {
      "id": "601723",
      "is_folded": false,
      "answerer": {
        "username": "hirozawayui",
        "uid": "98874"
      },
      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t清零政策不改，就会有越来越多的人们生活不下去，反抗的潜在力量就会更强\t\t</div>",
      "date": "2022-11-28",
      "agree_count": 1,
      "discussion_count": 0,
      "discussions": []
    },
    {
      "id": "601833",
      "is_folded": false,
      "answerer": {
        "username": "poetry",
        "uid": "103726"
      },
      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t抗议本身就不应该被报以直接推翻政权的想法，但这无疑会推动这一过程，看到人民警察和党员干部殴打群众并传播也会让大多没醒来的人醒来，习近平现在愈发下不来台了，政策只要没有转向的可能性，他们的统治就会越发不得人心，不管你喊的什么口号他到最后会陷入开枪镇压和向人民低头的两难境地，这是一针加速剂\t\t</div>",
      "date": "2022-11-28",
      "agree_count": 1,
      "discussion_count": 0,
      "discussions": []
    },
    {
      "id": "601692",
      "is_folded": false,
      "answerer": {
        "username": "rool",
        "uid": "94384"
      },
      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t没关系，当人们意识到和平抗争无效的时候，更多的激进行为会出现\t\t</div>",
      "date": "2022-11-27",
      "agree_count": 0,
      "discussion_count": 0,
      "discussions": []
    },
    {
      "id": "601702",
      "is_folded": false,
      "answerer": {
        "username": "止痛药",
        "uid": "52311"
      },
      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t抗议活动本来就三天熄火，举榔头也比举白纸强啊。\t\t</div>",
      "date": "2022-11-28",
      "agree_count": 0,
      "discussion_count": 0,
      "discussions": []
    },
    {
      "id": "601717",
      "is_folded": false,
      "answerer": {
        "username": "rstzh",
        "uid": "101827"
      },
      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t中国的抗议要有成就必须政治化！<br/>\n中国的抗议要有成就必须政治化！<br/>\n中国的抗议要有成就必须政治化！<br/>\n<br/>\n中国每年成片上万的零散抗议都不成气候就是因为太issue-specific！！必须政治化，直接target政权。中国人有造反起义的传统，不要低估中国人。\t\t</div>",
      "date": "2022-11-28",
      "agree_count": 0,
      "discussion_count": 0,
      "discussions": []
    },
    {
      "id": "601726",
      "is_folded": false,
      "answerer": {
        "username": "PCUSER2020",
        "uid": "38902"
      },
      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t很难熄火，熄火表示坐等被清算，谁敢随便熄火？很多事情开弓没有回头箭\t\t</div>",
